description:

SHIPPING INCLUDES GIFT BOX

Length: 136cm 
Width: 110cm
Weight: 535grams


Safety Tips:
Its beautiful to decorate your cot with comforters, quilts and pillows but please be aware to remove any comforters, quilts and pillows out of the cot before putting baby to sleep when under the age of 12 months.

name: JAZZI SNAZZY GIRAFFE BAG
description:
Kids are naturally playful and active. Luckily, there are a few things that can keep up with little kids busy and active lifestyle such as the easy to use kindy bags. They are both functional and trendy. Simple yet fashionable day care bags are sure to keep up with your childrens daily routine. Another quality bags that are equally useful are the library bags that are carefully hand crafted to ensure durability, made out of heavy duty canvas that can be gently hand washed to keep them in tip-top shape so your kids could always look great using them such as this featured bag. Bags like this are just great as a simple book bags or childrens library bags where they can carry a lot of their books and school stuff and yet still look cool and fun. It can even keep up with your kids outdoor activities as well and at the same time they can store a lot of their thingy-ma-jiggies in them. They can always be ready for any outdoor fun with their friends.  The bags simple and neat design is definitely a keeper! Any child, even the not so young will fall in love with this trendy bag.

Gentle hand wash only
Do not bleach

name: LOU LOU OVERNIGHT BAG
description:
Poppy Lou kids bags all belong to a collectable series of seven different fun designs, each with its own unique 3D critter. All playfully popping out from brightly coloured backgrounds of either striped, chequered, patchwork or plain patterns guaranteed to make your pride and joy stand out in the crowd.

All these little bags for little grown-ups are fully lined and perfect for carrying their library books, sleepover gear, swimming togs and shopping stuff and will certainly rock the street, beach or kindy as they proudly walk past.

Handmade looking from heavy duty, hand washable canvas, these hard wearing, happy-fashion bags are designed to stand the rigours of play life for years to come and still look really, really funky!
